{"tid":1437011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國家民航局向國泰航空發出重大航空安全風險警示","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:10:49.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91458f7c23a79729f0401ddc9a1684e85d953fc4","tid":1437011,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473694-20190809.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473694-20190809.htm&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=ba56cb9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473694-20190809.htm&h=f7873052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473694-20190809.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n國家民航局向國泰航空發出重大航空安全風險警示。<br />\n<br />\n民航局在內地微博發布，指國泰航空先後發生飛行人員參與暴力衝擊，被控暴動罪卻未被停止飛行活動，以及惡意洩露航班旅客資訊等事件，存在嚴重威脅航空安全的隱患，造成了惡劣社會影響，增加了香港至內地的輸入性航空安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n民航局對國泰明確提出三點要求，由星期六起，立即停止對所有參與和支持非法遊行示威、暴力衝擊活動，以及有過過激行為的人員，在飛往內地航班或執行與內地航空運輸活動相關的一切職務活動；<br />\n<br />\n另外，由星期日起，在所有飛往內地和飛越內地領空的機組人員的身份，在未經審核通過，不予接收有關航班；<br />\n<br />\n在下星期三前，向運行合格審定機構，報送公司加強內部管控、提升飛行安全和安保水準的措施。 <br />\n<br />\n民航局將視國泰航空對上述警示要求的執行情況，依法依規監管處置。"},{"pid":"5154f9839b0f165fb9ed26915e5b4355de066c0f","tid":1437011,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">不是行動，不推文回覆，謝謝</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ae58824d459f2bdfed6996cd1a6896c48ea97fae","tid":1437011,"uid":38974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"空姐都唔想飛大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3346e2b5aaa78a1bfb920275fe4bbd807c3b452a","tid":1437011,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae58824d459f2bdfed6996cd1a6896c48ea97fae","tid":1437011,"uid":38974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"空姐都唔想飛大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"無得飛內地線係獎勵定係懲罰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}